==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Air sickness
<hw>Air" sick"ness</hw>. <def>A vomiting or nauseous feeling similar to
seasickness experienced by passengers in aircraft; -- it is caused by
motion and distinguished from the effects of low air pressure, as it may
also occur in the pressurized cabins of large aircraft.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Air-slacked</ent>⟦br⟧
